	 <!-- Second section of the article-->
      <section id="lab-article-section-3">
        
        <div id="lab-article-section-3-icon" class="icon">
          <!-- Enclose the icon image for the section. -->
	  <img src="../images/theory.jpg" />
	</div>


        <!-- The heading for the section can be enclosed in a 
        div tag and shown with a <h2> tag -->
	<div id="lab-article-section-3-heading" class="heading">
	 Theory
	</div>
				
	<!-- Write the section content inside a paragraph 
        element, You can also include images with <img> tag -->
        <div id="lab-article-section-3-content" class="content">
<strong>
	<table>
	<tr>
	<p>
	Light is made up of photons. The energy of each photon is given by<br/>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="images/pe4.jpg"><br/><br><br>
	where <i>h</i> is the Plank's constant and <i>f</i> is the frequency of photon.<br/><br/>
	When a photon strikes a metal surface, some of its energy is transferred to the electron of the metal atom. It is called a photoelctron. Some of this energy is used by the photoelectron to break away from the metal surface and the rest is converted to its kinetic energy.<br/><br/>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="images/pe1.jpg"><br/><br><br>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="images/pe2.jpg"><br/><br><br>
	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="images/pe3.jpg"><br/><br><br>
	where &phi; is the work function characteristic to the metal and <i>f<sub>0</sub></i> is the threshold frequency necessary for photocurrent.<br/>
	
	</p></tr>
	<br><br><br><br>
	</table>
	</strong>
	</div>
</section>


